snippet.textDisplay:
Love it. Love it. LOVE IT!!  I saw the original video version in a comedy club, but the sound was poor, so I'm glad they did a better version.
And all the stuff she says - and the way she acts at the end - so very true.
I hope they find a cure or a vaccine soon, otherwise we are in for a very long and frustrating battle.
